content.rendered:
OUR SERVICES

Making the world a smaller place

  • EXPRESS PARCEL
  • PARTIAL-TRUCKLOAD FREIGHT
  • TRUCKLOAD FREIGHT
  • CROSS-BORDER SERVICES
  • SUPPLY CHAIN SERVICES

CROSS-BORDER SERVICES

Our cross-border offering provides door-to-door, port-to-port express parcel services as well as air cargo to and from India. Our operations are powered by our global shipping service, “Starfleet”, where we follow a“string of pearls” strategy, integrating global networks and airlines on the same platform, providing single-window visibility into express and freight global shipping to shippers. We have established a reciprocal relationship with FedEx in order to expand our coverage across key international markets.

Our capabilities include an integrated network of express and freight solutions coupled with supplementary solutions of tech-enabled tracking, an in-house regulatory team for proactive clearance support, and a dedicated customer servicing team.

SERVICES

Global B2C and B2B Shipping

Sea and Air Cargo Shipping

Air Express Shipping

International Fulfilment Centers

Cross-border Returns Management

International Channel Integration
and Management

TECHNOLOGY SERVICES

Real-time Cargo Visibility

Online CHA and Gateway

Management

Real Time Visibility of Origin

Destination Clearance

Contact Us
